name: Ginoa
description: "Ginoa is the first AI-based NFT Expert. It provides the best price for the NFT collections you are interested in, taking into account historical sales data and rarity characteristics. And its recent goal is to price all NFTs. This service is offered completely free of charge. Ginoa scans all NFTs for sale for you. It presents those that are sold at a lower price than the price given by artificial intelligence as an opportunity. It does this automatically every day and notifies you about opportunities. Ginoa aims to give prices to all NFT collectibles produced."
